          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>HERE'S a thing in the <hi rend="italics">East</hi>, that inhabits the <hi rend="italics">South</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-2" n="2">Which Swallows the Ocean, without Throat or a Mouth,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-3" n="3">It's made up of Opium, with Lungs from the <hi rend="italics">Moon</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-4" n="4">And never can speak, without aid of a Spoon</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-5" n="5">The <hi rend="italics">D</hi>octors are drunk, when they think to define</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-6" n="6">The Properties various, twixt me and the Vine.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-7" n="7">Howsoever this ease, to their stomachs I give,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-8" n="8">I die to relieve them, they die whilst I live,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-9" n="9">You know all the Secrets, that are hid in the Town,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-10" n="10">And <hi rend="italics">Legerdemain</hi> will show for a Crown,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-11" n="11">Why then two Shillings more, I'le give you my Leech</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-S172S508-line-12" n="12">If this you unriddle in Writing or Speech.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
